import math

def calculate_earliest_arrival_times(N, csf):
    results = []
    for i in range(N):
        ans = 1
        for j in range(i, N - 1):
            c = csf[j][0]
            s = csf[j][1]
            f = csf[j][2]
            ans = max(s, math.ceil(ans / f) * f) + c
        results.append(ans)
    return results
